title: A letter agreed unto, and subscribed by the gentlemen, ministers, freeholders and seamen of the county of Suffolk, presented to His Excellency, the Lord Generall Monck
author: Albemarle, George Monck, Duke of, 1608-1670.
notes: "This letter was delivered at St. Albans, Jan. 28, 1659, by Sir Henry Felton, barronet, Robert Brook, and William Bloys, Esquires."
Reproduction of original in Huntington Library.
